 2023-09602023-09-28ISI
ActBudget Implementation Act, 2022, No. 1
SubjectOrder Fixing January 22, 2024 as the Day on Which Sections 431 to 433 of the Budget Implementation Act, 2022, No. 1 Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing January 22, 2024 as the day on which sections 431 to 433 of the BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2022, NO. 1, Chapter 10 of the Statutes of Canada, 2022, COME INTO FORCE in order to require certain corporations to send information on its individuals with significant control to the director appointed under the Canada Business Corporations Act and to allow the director to provide all or part of that information to an investigative body, the Financial Transactions and Reports Analysis Centre of Canada or any prescribed entity.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/
